@node "Was_txt" "Was ist das ?"


No...this is not a new clock !  Not a normal clock.  This clock has been
created to show the internet time called Swatch Beats invented by Swatch.
This internet-time is worldwide the same.

How long is a Beat ? A Day is divided into 1000 Beats. One Beat stands for 1
minute and 26.4 seconds.

I searched within the Aminet for a nice programm that is able to show me the
current Time in Beats.  But I didn't like, what I found, so I made my own.
:-)


                                @{"Okay !" link "Main" 0}
@endnode

