@node "Pref1" "Pref 1"


This menus are available:


@{"Project" link "Project" 0} @{"Pref 1" link "Pref1" 0} @{"P 2" link "Pref2" 0} @{"P 3" link "Pref3" 0} @{"Precision" link "Precision" 0} @{"Layouts" link "Layouts" 0} @{"Konfiguration" link "Konfiguration" 0}
        @{u}      @{uu}.


        DST On  - Daylight Saving Time on

        DST Off - Daylight Saving Time off


The dates for the DST 1999 are: 28.03.99 - 31.10.99 If anybody knows the
dates for 2000 please send me  a @{"e-mail" link "VonWEM_TXT" 0}
